WOMAN (on phone):
Hey, Mickey. I need you
to watch the kids.

22:06.192 --> 22:07.992
-We had to flee the country.
-(groans)

22:09.528 --> 22:11.762
â™ª (humming)

22:11.764 --> 22:13.030
Whoa! Aaah!

22:13.032 --> 22:13.964
(loud thud)

22:13.966 --> 22:16.133
-I think she's dead.
-(screams)

22:16.135 --> 22:19.270
-What's everybody
thinkin' for dinner?
-We've just eaten breakfast.

22:19.272 --> 22:21.539
Well, uh... good morning.

22:23.275 --> 22:25.876
-She's a danger
to these children.
-The kids are fine!

22:25.878 --> 22:27.978
Can I have
some more ice cream?

22:27.980 --> 22:29.613
Aaah! Aaah!

22:29.615 --> 22:30.881
