22:34.486 --> 22:36.387
(beeping)

22:36.389 --> 22:38.522
Nicole.
Get to the attic.

22:38.524 --> 22:41.125
No matter what you hear,
don't make a sound.

22:41.827 --> 22:43.527
(breathing quietly)

22:44.663 --> 22:46.464
(Nicole breathing shakily)

22:51.670 --> 22:52.737
-(phone rings)
-Carter?

22:52.739 --> 22:54.538
-They're here.
-My God.

